organic.title: St. Joseph's Hospital | Tucson AZ - Carondelet Health Network
organic.snippet: Established in 1961, St. Joseph's Hospital is a Level I Trauma Center serving Tucson and Southern Arizona. It is also home to the Carondelet Neurological Institute and the Carondelet Joint Replacement Center. Our 451-bed hospital provides one of the region's most comfortable labor and delivery units.
